title: Argentina Faces Presidential Runoff: Massa and Milei Vie for Leadership Amid Economic Tensions
description: This past weekend in Argentina, a vote for the country’s next president led to a runoff between Finance Minister Sergio Massa of the Unión por la Patria party and libertarian candidate Javier Milei of the La Libertad Avanza party. In the Sunday vote, Massa received 37% while Milei garnered 30%. Massa, Milei Eye Victory in […]

title: Extensive data collection on crypto users proposal by IRS
description: In a move that has sparked significant debate and concern within the cryptocurrency community, the Internal Revenue Service (IRS) is proposing new regulations that would require crypto service providers to collect extensive data about their users.
